## Objective
Integrate PurchaseButton with the Stripe Checkout flow using existing remote functions, handling authentication, redirect construction, and error states for a complete purchase experience.

## System Context
The Ecom-API worker (port 42072) and @codex/purchase services are fully implemented. Remote functions in `lib/remote/checkout.remote.ts` provide form-based and command-based checkout patterns. This task wires the UI components to the existing backend.

## Files
